Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.16,0:21:52.87,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(333,584)}無表情に流れながら
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.87,0:21:57.54,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(333,584)}両手から零れてゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.54,0:22:01.71,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(333,584)}ゆらゆら揺れてて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.71,0:22:04.51,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(333,584)}知らずにいた
